column2: "Ah... <%me>. Ummm, mind if I say something strange?"
"It feels like something's about to happen."
"I don't know what's going to happen exactly, but... with everyone rushing around lately, there must be something."
"I know because I've been observing everyone all this time."
"Plus, it's just my instincts, but... I feel that something's happening."
"Is it anxiety...? I don't really know myself, but, that doesn't..."
"...I'm sorry, saying something so out of line. But, no matter what happens, we'll be together, anyway."
